data.description: Super Clean move in ready 4-bed, 2.5-bath with New LVP flooring, carpet plus freshly paint. Revel in the open-concept living, ideal for seamless entertaining. Upstairs unveils a spacious loft, 4 generous bedrooms, and a convenient laundry room. Step into a vast backyard oasis, fully fenced for privacy - perfect for play, relaxation, or tending to your raised garden beds. Nestled in a welcoming neighborhood within the esteemed Lake Stevens school district, this home offers proximity to shops, Seattle Premium Outlet Mall, restaurants and more. Appliances included. Your dream of homeownership awaits, just in time for the holidays and ready to kick off the New Year in style.
